#{{{ WANT TO ADD/EDIT A COLOR? READ THIS FIRST...

# (This is my custom color scheme, created 2025-07-29)
# (The structure of this file is based on https://github.com/seebi/dircolors-solarized.)

# TO ADD/EDIT A COLOR, first add/edit it to ~/.config/yazi/theme.toml
# The reasons are twofold:
  #- convenience of quick previews in yazi
  #- it's easier to edit this file to match yazi/theme.toml than vice versa

#}}}

